			</p>
			<div class="sm:flex flex-1 gap-14">
				<div class="sm:w-[800px]">
					<Image
						src={firstImage}
						alt="日本街景"
						width={1100}
						sizes={inlineSizes}
						class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
					/>
				</div>
				<p class="text-justify items-center flex">整个城市在夜晚显得格外静谧，街道上零星的行人走过，仿佛每一步都在记录这座城市的过往...</p>
